cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.SY 

This paper deals with the validation of neural network controllers for computer vision problems, which suggests that it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), robotics (cs.RO), and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper specifically focuses on the use of adaptive stress testing to validate the controllers, which further supports the likelihood of these sub-categories.
